OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,FA fraudster who bought a house and a
OL,7,Fsupercar after conning more than 600
OL,8,Fpeople out of about #9 million has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FDeclan Nowell, 31, promised lucrative
OL,12,Freturns to victims who believed he was
OL,13,Finvesting funds into foreign currency
OL,14,Fmarkets.
OL,16,FInstead the money was being used to
OL,17,Foperate a so-called Ponzi scheme,
OL,18,Fwhere money from new customers was
OL,19,Fbeing paid to existing investors.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
