FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,FNowell pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,7,Ffraud by abuse of position and one
OL,8,Fcount of operating an unauthorised,
OL,9,Funregulated investment scheme.
OL,11,FHe was jailed for eight years and a
OL,12,Fmonth and was banned from holding a
OL,13,Fdirector position for 10 years.
OL,15,FDet Con Paul Twidale, of Humberside
OL,16,FPolice, said: "Nowell's actions were
OL,17,Freckless. He made a calculated
OL,18,Fdecision to repeatedly mislead his
OL,19,Fclients.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
