OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,F"Despite having numerous opportunities
OL,7,Fto halt the illegal operation, he
OL,8,Fchose to continue the deception, all
OL,9,Fdriven by personal greed."
OL,11,FThe force's economic crime unit began
OL,12,Fin investigation into Nowell's company
OL,13,FInvesting4You in 2021 after several
OL,14,Freports from members of the public who
OL,15,Fhad been unable to withdraw funds held
OL,16,Fin investment accounts.
OL,18,FOfficers found he had only deposited a
OL,19,Ftiny fraction of #9m, with trades
OL,20,Fresulting in losses.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
