PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,FNowell, of Scunthorpe, had spent #1m
OL,7,Fon a McLaren car, a house and designer
OL,8,Fclothing.
OL,10,FDet Con Twidale said: "It came to
OL,11,Flight that his investment company was
OL,12,Fnot accredited and operating
OL,13,Fillegally, not only through operating
OL,14,Fwithout licence but also through
OL,15,Fmanipulating the figures displayed in
OL,16,Finvestors accounts.
OL,26,@rD@WOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,F"Throughout this investigation, Nowell
OL,7,Fmaintained a ridiculous and
OL,8,Finconceivable stance that somewhere
OL,9,F#28 million was sitting in a mystery
OL,10,Fpot that would prove his enterprise
OL,11,Fwas legitimate and enable all
OL,12,Finvestors to be paid back completely."
OL,14,FHe added: "When concerned customers
OL,15,Fenquired about Nowell's professional
OL,16,Faccreditation, he repeatedly claimed
OL,17,Fit was pending.
OL,19,F"By operating without essential
OL,20,Fregulatory approval, he was committing
OL,21,Fa crime from day one of operation."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
