PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780341071
OL,3,C'Callous' investment fraudster who
OL,4,Cconned 600 victims out of #9m jailed
OL,6,FVivienne Hartley, specialist
OL,7,Fprosecutor for the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService, said: "Declan Nowell was
OL,9,Foperating a callous scam targeting the
OL,10,Fpublic. Many people lost their hard
OL,11,Fearned money because of Nowell's
OL,12,Fgreed, fake investment schemes and
OL,13,Ffalse promises."
OL,15,FEfforts to recover Nowell's proceeds
OL,16,Fof crime remain ongoing.
OL,26,@pD@POU
